---
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background:#FFFFFF; padding:128px 24px;">
  <p class="absolute top-4 left-6 select-none pointer-events-none"
     style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-weight:900; font-size:clamp(60px,12vw,140px); letter-spacing:-0.05em; opacity:0.04; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1B5EBE,#4A90D9); -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent; background-clip:text; line-height:1; pointer-events:none; user-select:none;">
    FUKUOKA × AI
  </p>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

    <div>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1B5EBE,#4A90D9); -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent; background-clip:text; margin-bottom:20px;" class="reveal">
        外部CAIOサービス · 福岡
      </p>

      <h1 class="mb-6 reveal" style="line-height:1.1;">
        <span style="font-family:'Inter','Noto Sans JP',sans-serif; font-weight:900; font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,56px); letter-spacing:-0.03em; color:#1A1A1A; display:block;">
          AIのことなら、
        </span>
        <span style="font-family:'Inter','Noto Sans JP',sans-serif; font-weight:900; font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,56px); letter-spacing:-0.03em; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1B5EBE 0%,#4A90D9 40%,#C8A15A 60%,#1B5EBE 100%); background-size:300% auto; -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent; background-clip:text; animation:shimmer 4s linear infinite; display:block;">
          お任せください。
        </span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mb-10 reveal" style="font-size:17px; color:#6B6B6B; font-weight:300; line-height:1.9; max-width:520px;">
        外部CAIOという働き方で、企業に入り込んでAI化を伴走します。<br />
        福岡の中小企業のAI活用を、現場から支えます。
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 reveal">
        <a href="https://lin.ee/VOiIxYB"
           target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
           style="background:#06C755; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.05em; padding:14px 24px; border-radius:4px;">
          💬 LINEで無料相談
        </a>
        <a href="/service"
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
           style="border:1px solid #E5E5E5; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.05em; padding:14px 24px; border-radius:4px;">
          サービスを見る →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="w-full flex items-center justify-center flex-col gap-3"
           style="height:360px; border:1px solid rgba(200,161,90,0.3); background:#FFFFFF; border-radius:8px;">
        <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none">
          <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="28" stroke="#1B5EBE" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 3" opacity="0.3"/>
          <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="16" stroke="#1B5EBE" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.2"/>
          <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="6" fill="#1B5EBE" opacity="0.3"/>
        </svg>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; color:#1B5EBE; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.15em; opacity:0.6;">AI × 中小企業</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
